      "raw_text": "Judge KEENAN, has been asked to\ndesignate. on Monday next. some per-\nson in Elack River Falls. Wis. to\ntake the deposition of Mrs. Sarah\nMay Wright, whose husband was kill\ned last November by being run over\nby Northern Pacific train at Gem,\nIdaho. Mrs. Wright and daughter\nhave brought action against the com\npany for $4,000 and the deposition\nis in lieu of testimony at the APP\npreaching trial"
    }
